                                    <div class="byline">
				<p uri="/liahona/2005/05/34.p2" class="" id="p2">&Eacute;lder Stephen B. Oveson</p>
				<p uri="/liahona/2005/05/34.p3" class="" id="p3">De los Setenta</p>
